query:
SELECT t.ticket, t.symbol, t.type, t.status, t.profit, t.openTime, t.createdAt
FROM trades t
JOIN users u ON t.userId = u.id
WHERE u.email = 'adm1@sentra.com'
ORDER BY t.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
